company profile for choo bee metal industries bhd x edition india africa américa latina عربي argentina brasil canada  deutschland españa france india italia  méxico россия united kingdom united states profile choo bee metal industries bhd chookl related topics stock quotesbasic materialssteel overview news key developments people charts financials analysts chookl on kuala lumpur stock exchange myr pm ist change  chg rm  prev close rm open rm days high rm days low rm volume  avg vol  wk high rm wk low rm full description choo bee metal industries berhad is engaged in the processing of steel coils into steel products fabrication of steel products and trading of hardware products the company operates through two segments trading and manufacturing the trading segment deals in hardware and construction materials the manufacturing segment is engaged in the processing of steel coils into steel products and fabrication of steel products the company manufactures steel products for oil and gas application building and construction industries trading of hardware products such as beams channels mild steel plates flat bars angle bars stainless steel products and other building materials as well as provision of steel servicing such as slitting and shearing of coils it offers various products such as welded steel pipe  galvanized iron pipe carbon steel pipe for ordinary piping carbon steel tube for machine structural purpose window pipe galvanized steel conduit pipe and decor  string pipe » full overview of chookl company address choo bee metal industries bhd wisma soon teik aun jalan bendaipoh      p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation cheng hai soon  han leong tan  sieng tzi lee  cheng boon soon  hean hooi soon  » more officers  directors choo bee metal industries bhd news » more chookl news related topics stock quotesbasic materialssteel choo bee metal industries bhd chookl people  reuterscom x edition united states africa américa latina عربي ar